{"tid":2070930,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"街工同白頭佬我話你知","createTime":"2020-06-19T12:35:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-20T05:37:00.000Z","uid":11097,"like":61,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"0f5a24154005da173ab48cc7114937ee385ee693","tid":2070930,"uid":11097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T12:35:21.000Z","msg":"屌你老母棄權做主席果單野都未同你計<br />\n就係因為你怕事間接令到大口狗當選，咁多人俾人<br />\nDQ<br />\n<br />\n到7.1又想扮偉大做肉盾，屌你永遠都唔撚企係後生果邊<br />\n講難聽啲你根本同甲級戰犯冇撚分別，功績冇仲做豬隊友，我直情懷疑你個閪黨係共諜呀<br />\n<br />\n時代唔撚同咗啦屌你老母，係呀你地Out撚咗啦<br />\n國難當前，你地仲要恬不知恥貪圖高薪，磨爛蓆賴死唔走！<br />\n得！你唔撚走吖嘛，你想選吖嘛，好吖你地選呀<br />\n<br />\n我地一票都唔撚會投你，我地區選可以令姐姐個垃圾廢黨全軍盡墨，我地一樣有能力令你你街工一樣下場！ 咪撚以為我垛講笑，呢場仗唔撚係同你講玩，味以為可以好似上次咁側側膊我屌你老母<br />\n<br />\n你唔配合就拭目以待<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9e5e8ad7029ca7364158153a002f6b18ad28769","tid":2070930,"uid":11097,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T12:36:01.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>一票不投甲級政棍戰犯街工</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"2d5b434d3f6afae53e5af283f10d4c9b2e479bcc","tid":2070930,"uid":11097,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T12:37:19.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>一票不投甲級政棍戰犯街工</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"9c7e28c3b7b7fb28a7b6f92a192323c852e79c3e","tid":2070930,"uid":11097,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T12:37:32.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>一票不投甲級政棍戰犯街工</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"d53f03450f7078db7502b2238cc3111353fcb9f2","tid":2070930,"uid":11097,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T12:38:14.000Z","msg":"<span style